name: Atlete Timberland Delphiville
properties: Atlete me lëkurë sintetike dhe material të qëndrueshëm ReBOTL që përmban së paku 50% plastikë të recikluar. Ka shtresë me densitet të dyfishtë dhe teknologji OrthoLite
properties_en: Upper made with synthetic leather and durable ReBOTL fabric containing at least 50% recycled plastic  Durable ReBOTL fabric lining made with at least 50% recycled plastic  Dual-density lightweight EVA midsole cushioning  Lightweight and breathable OrthoLi
composition_en: Upper made with ReBOTL fabric and synthetic leather  100% PET laces  ReBOTL fabric lining
